column5: The lake sure has changed in last 5 days
Big change. Cooler temps and some wind. Temps now 64.  	Can’t buy a walleye.
Didn't see anything higher then 72 yesterday on Lower Buck and that was in the wind swept bays.  Lots and lots of spawning carp in the shallows.
North channel was running 58.5 today. My dog is not happy with no fish.
My lake is 63f and hazy from the smoke. Crankbait bite is on...
